---
title: Middle Eastern Pork & Currant Filo Rolls with Garden Salad & Mint Yoghurt
description: These savoury cigars are the ultimate finger food! Layers of flaky filo encase a delicious spiced pork mince filling with pops of sweetness from currants and onion. Paired with a refreshing salad and fragrant mint yoghurt, this dish is perfectly balanced and sure to satisfy.

